Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:42.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\be2\pos(358,388)\fs34}Jackson Setouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:37.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Jackson Setouchi. He's like a boss of Year 1 at Bass High.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Due to his great physical strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he's also known as "Bass' King of Destruction."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:52.46,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,0)\be2}Akio Takejo (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Akio Takejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Setouchi's right-hand man, the one he trusts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bass High's Year 1 #2 man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:52.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}It's even said that Bass doesn't\N make a move without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:59.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs24\be2\pos(358,390)}Year 1 Students Regular Meeting at Bass High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Unless we do something,\N Cromartie will keep looking down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our Year 2 doesn't stand up to Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's why they look down on us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Should we also beat up\N our Year 2 at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But we have a tradition\N of respecting seniority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if Year 2 is pathetic,\N we, as Year 1, shouldn't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cromartie's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:22.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Particularly, I heard that you can't stop\Nthat Takenouchi guy when he snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's about time for Bass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,to end its history of being below\N Cromartie with our, Year 1's, hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His nose hair's sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we should do it by ourselves?\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not something that \Nwe can decide just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:45.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But upon the honor\N of Bass' name, we have to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,if we are to fight against Cromartie\Nor if we should back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's definitely sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cromartie... It sure is scary there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's bugging me so much\N I can't focus on the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! He noticed it!\NMy prayer may have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I can relax and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the... It moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But think about it calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our fighting power is\N definitely as good as theirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:18.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Thinking scientifically,\Nthere's no way it can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he's touching his nose again,\Nwhich could mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There are more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Akio Takejo's nose hair was sticking out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And there were going to be more and more.
