Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(0,350)}Cromartie Municipal High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:42.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama, was school\N always this boring and dull?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:46.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's how school is, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When we're at this sensitive stage in our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,being really bored is, in a way,\Nsimilar to being tortured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I say it as a delinquent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:04:00.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But developing such patience is also\N important in preparing for the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:04.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Basically, school is a place to study,\Nso it can't possibly be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:08.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our school is a school for badasses, but in\Nthat sense, it's the same as other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:13.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'm fed up\N with this familiar scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, being bored means\N that we're peaceful and happy, so....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wish something really\Nsurprising would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I didn't know Freddie had a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:30.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida, didn't you see it\N in front of the restroom before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now getting back to the earlier topic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Delinquents are often mistaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but school is a place where you study,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:41.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,not a place where you expect\Nsomething fun or surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:45.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I think other schools\N could be more interesting and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You sound like a child\Nwho envies what others have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:54.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A friend of someone I know goes to a school \Nthat seems to be very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:59.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you see, that friend is just exaggerating.\NHis school is normal, just like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, everyone's bored,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:05.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but they try to convince themselves that\Nthe environment they're in is interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because they don't want to think that they're\Nthe only one who's spending a boring life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, every school's the same.\NThey are normal, just like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\N but I just want some excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:21.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you bluntly. There isn't even one such\Nexcitement here. I can say that with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lero Liro Lero Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a wild horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez... It's extremely imprudent\N to come to school by horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:43.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I still think other schools are\Nmore exciting and interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:47.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it? Any school is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:52.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,People who say school's fun are so bored\Nthat they feel even stupid stuff is interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,or they convince themselves that theirs is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're saying that\N we shouldn't bother complaining how boring it is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,when it's supposed to be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, our school's too normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&\pos(358,433)}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Normal is fine. What's wrong with normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not really expecting anything that incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:14.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All I want is a little something\Nthat'll give me a bit of a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,An incident that'll give us a bit of a laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!\N Maeda's being bitten by a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!\N Maeda's being bitten by a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!\N Maeda's being bitten by a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)\fnArtificeSSK\c&HBD36B6&\bord0.6\fs36\blur0.5\pos(358,95)}At Least It's a Battle\N Without Honor or Humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Bass High School Gym Storage Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna fudgin' kill me, do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen,\N since you're an important hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? A hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:07.23,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Jackson Setouchi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}We're gonna lure Cromartie's Takenouchi\Nto our Bass High by using you as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Today's the end for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You bastard! That's a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who cares about dirty tricks\Nwhen fighting, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our guys are heading to Cromartie right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:19.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We got a call from Aki.\N Seems like he got to Cro-High.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, give the phone to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:31.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,390)\be3\fnSweet as candy\b0}Jackson Setouchi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}It's me, Setouchi.\N There's a guy named Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Call him out and tell him this:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:36.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"We have Maeda, so come to Bass High alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:37.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.23,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(368.196,391)}Bass High No. 2        Akio Takejo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're at Cromartie's front gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(172.203,64)\c&H4D7B96&\3c&H3A455D&\bord2\be2}Cromartie \NHigh School
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and we just ran into something disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Footprints! And they aren't\Njust normal footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:53.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're horse hooves!\NAnd they're as big as elephant's feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Make up your mind\N if it's a horse or an elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I said it was a horse, didn't I?!\NIt's not an elephant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's a huge horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's so huge, as if it may not be a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Calm down. This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't explain well over the phone.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I certainly can't understand\N it at all over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! Does your school have a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Akira Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's a guy who comes to school by horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnAveria Sans\bord0\blur0.5\shad0\c&H4A473F&\fs34\frz19.5\frx4\fry2\pos(200.525,281)}Talk
