Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell! I found another disturbing thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a vending machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's a vending machine\Nin front of the school gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We have a vending machine in\Nour cafeteria too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it. This isn't\Na regular vending machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell's that vending machine like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:51.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, listen carefully!\N This vending machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:51.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnGilles' Comic Font\fs34\bord0\blur0.5\shad0\c&H191944&\pos(339.873,485)}Guts
