Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have a slot for 100 yen coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello.
