Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's probably not a vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell! I found something\Neven more disturbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's a gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:20.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it's someone with a face like gorilla's, \Nany school has at least one such guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone\N with a face like a gorilla's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&\pos(358,433)}Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No! Not someone like a gorilla, but a real gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.\N You're saying there's a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:32.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But just the same, that gorilla's\N wearing a school uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You moron! There's no way a gorilla'd\Nbe wearing a uniform, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,ls there a gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:42.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There is, but I don't know if\Nhe's one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:49.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell! An even more\N disturbing thing has shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:56.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come on, there's no way that something\Nmore disturbing than a gorilla appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What could be more\N disturbing than a gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Surely you're not gonna tell me that\Nthere's an alien or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And did you find Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, he isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I've started feeling like\N I don't care about Takenouchi any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why are there aliens,\N but no Takenouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I go home now?
