Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's also a next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, the night's wearing on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but please bear with us a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Maeda and Freddie's horse don't get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
